Interface Map2.Entry<X,Y,V>

Enclosing interface:
Map2<X,Y,V>
public static interface Map2.Entry<X,Y,V>

A map entry (key1-key2-value pair). The Map.entrySet method returns a collection view of the map, whose elements are of this class. You can use an iterator or a loop to scan through the entries.

See Also:
